<p><big><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">Parseval&#039;s theorem:</span><big> </big></big></p>
<table style="width: 696px; height: 90px;" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">
